// Tutorial 5 — Rewriting rules
//
// The power of BPscript: symbols get rewritten by rules.
// S -> A B means S becomes A then B.
// Then A and B are rewritten by their own rules.
//
// This is how you build structure:
//   S = whole piece
//   A, B = phrases
//   Their rules define the notes.

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:browser
@mm:90

S -> Phrase1 Phrase2 Phrase1

Phrase1 -> C4 E4 G4 E4
Phrase2 -> F4 A4 G4 F4 E4 D4
